  "texts": [
    "Although the order in which the trials for each crime were presented was randomized, we forced the first trial that each participant saw to never be an incorrect trial in order to build some confidence in the AI system.",
    "The experimental manipulation took place in Steps 1 and 2.",
    "In the AIsupport→Judgment group, in Step 1, participants viewed the AI system's assessment (low or high probability of guilt, as in the Experiment 1).",
    "In the incorrect cases, the AI assessment was incongruent with the previously presented testimonies and suggested the opposite verdict.",
    "As in Experiment 1, participants were asked on the same screen whether they wanted to confirm the AI assessment or modify it."
  ],
